comments.text:
Now I ain't no big city YouTube interpreter; but it seems as though it was 
the hallucinogenic manifestation of her guilt trying to have her face the 
truth. She'd shut off that traumatic part of her life. If that was how 
she'd met her boyfriend, it would be the guilt utilising her happier 
memories of their relationship. Otherwise, it was merely an easy way to 
make her face the truth without letting her run beforehand. That's just my 
opinion though, make of that part as you will.
